  "session": "2026RS",
  "identifier": "SB 52",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to ensuring fair permitting and licensing practices.",
  "abstract": "Create new sections of KRS Chapter 61 to prohibit public agencies from denying permits or licenses for reasons not specified by law; implement a 30-day time frame for ruling on applications for a permit or license if no time frame is otherwise specified by law; establish procedures for applications for a permit or license which are not ruled upon during the applicable time frame or are denied; for appeal process.",
